WReminder
Powered by ezWhy.com

How to install
1. Run WReminder_Setup.exe.
2. Follow the setup wizard.
3. Open WReminder from the Desktop shortcut or Start Menu: ezWhy > WReminder.

How to exit from tray
1. Right-click the WReminder icon in the Windows system tray.
2. Choose Thoat to fully exit the app.

How to update
1. Download the new version from ezWhy.com.
2. Exit WReminder from the system tray.
3. Run the new installer.
4. Your reminder data will be kept.

Data storage
WReminder stores reminder data and logs in:
%APPDATA%\ezWhy\WReminder

